OL,5,G2100 Trauma Room One
OL,6,     FA man arrives in theatre with
OL,7,     Fagonising back pain and doctors
OL,8,     Fsuspect a cancerous tumour is
OL,9,     Fcompressing his spinal cord. He
OL,10,     Fneeds an urgent operation using a
OL,11,     Fhi-tech robot to remove it. (Ep3)
